1
00:00:00,333 --> 00:00:01,059
Batman?

2
00:00:01,100 --> 00:00:02,100
Robin?

3
00:00:10,629 --> 00:00:12,610
Somebody's been doing some redecorating.

4
00:00:14,770 --> 00:00:16,030
What are you doing here?

5
00:00:20,510 --> 00:00:22,070
It's kind of a long story.

6
00:00:23,470 --> 00:00:24,470
Whoa!

7
00:00:24,530 --> 00:00:26,270
Let's not get off on the wrong foot here.

8
00:00:26,530 --> 00:00:28,770
Because that's one foot you don't want to
step on.

9
00:00:33,390 --> 00:00:36,590
Batman's not going to be happy when he
hears how you've been treating his guests.

10
00:00:36,650 --> 00:00:38,830
And you really don't want to see Batman
unhappy.

11
00:00:39,250 --> 00:00:41,490
First, we don't have guests here.

12
00:00:41,730 --> 00:00:43,610
And second, I'm Batman.

13
00:00:44,130 --> 00:00:45,610
And I'm Beyoncé.

14
00:00:46,510 --> 00:00:48,650
Well, whoever you are, you don't belong
here.

15
00:00:55,210 --> 00:00:56,390
Getting sloppy!

